nstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=80k6gzYtLn_8_018HJQA6A&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_AfymGyjSjeqUYFEUQNsiCFIn6KbHM4iRvYnKV9hwDpm52A&amp;oe=69CA32C0" alt="Slide 3 fra @philosophybreak" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/438088974_813771884139058_1390673064265091955_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzM0ODk3NTUwOTMwNTQ3NzI0NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTA4MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=5CFhHTHCrTsQ7kNvwHWLpFq&amp;_nc_oc=Adp3nAvG1A3mDZo8Mk1NqpkaOE-li-SLfoJpvwzVodBn2qaJ5zW3wbGG0L7c9k1a97o&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=80k6gzYtLn_8_018HJQA6A&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afwh-FbCbJeVLOKw_SdcsVZl-kVX4dXIYOwfkj2sm-4HQQ&amp;oe=69CA26C0" alt="Slide 4 fra @philosophybreak" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (5 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@philosophybreak</strong></p><p>My name’s Jack, I live in London, and with Philosophy Break I’m aiming to do two things for you:<br/>
<br/>
1. Help you quickly understand the most powerful, mind-opening ideas in philosophy.<br/>
<br/>
2. Offer clear next steps for when you want to further explore a particular philosopher or topic.<br/>
<br/>
Having spent 15+ years studying philosophy (picking up a master’s degree along the way), my aim is to distill everything I’ve learned (and continue to learn) from my meandering philosophical education into ultra-concise materials, available to you here and beyond.<br/>
<br/>
My hope is to provide shortcuts to the ‘good stuff’, and offer clear direction for when you want to dive deeper.<br/>
<br/>
I do this through social media, but primarily through my website and newsletter at philosophybreak.com, where I distill &amp; discuss one famous philosophical idea per week.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you very much for reading and engaging with Philosophy Break.<br/>
<br/>
If you’ve enjoyed my content here, I think you’ll get a lot out of the newsletter. It’s totally free, and you can join thousands of like-minded thinkers who discuss philosophy each week. I love hearing from you, and read and respond to every message.<br/>
<br/>
Simply hit the link in my bio to sign up 👉 @philosophybreak 💭⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣<br/>
<br/>
#philosophy #philosophystudent #philosophymajor</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5584BtIlEb/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
